OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDyfed-Powys Police: Chief  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwants one Welsh force      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Wales' four police forces should be    
OL,6, scrapped and replaced with a single    
OL,7, nationwide service, according to       
OL,8, Dyfed-Powys Police's new chief         
OL,9, constable.                             
OL,11,FFormer Cleveland Police boss Dr Richard
OL,12,FLewis has said this should be in place 
OL,13,Fby 2030.                               
OL,15,F"(If) the Americans can put a man on   
OL,16,Fthe moon in eight years, I think we can
OL,17,Funify four police services," he said.  
OL,19,FThe Home Office said the existing      
OL,20,Fstructure meant everyone had a direct  
OL,21,Fsay on policing in their area.         
